@skathire @pabeda1 My read of the point estimates from the Iceland lp(a) chart...

-risk is modest at the 80th percentile (~55nmol/L), CAD odds ratio ~1.12.

-CAD OR ~1.7x at ~215nmol/L, ~top 2.5 percentile

-CAD odds ratio >2x at >~270nmol/L, roughly top 0.5 %ile (~1 in 180)
